    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather. This collector-grade example is powered by the S54B32 3.2L high-revving inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. To ensure mechanical longevity, the high-pressure VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Beisan seals and the rod bearings have been replaced with VAC coated shells. The rear subframe\u2014a known structural pain point\u2014has been proactively reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, coupled with a factory limited-slip differential. Every bushing remains compliant, and the chassis is anchored by Bilstein B6 dampers. This vehicle is free of any fluid seepage or electrolytic corrosion, representing the pinnacle of atmospheric M-division engineering.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
