      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, finished in its original, high-gloss factory paint without a single swirl mark or stone chip. Inside, the cabin retains that 'new car' scent, with supple, unblemished leather seating and a dashboard free of any UV wear or scratches. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates with the precision of the day it rolled off the assembly line. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and backed by a comprehensive service history, this car has never seen rain or snow. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this is a collector-grade find for the discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 43500.0,
