      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this\u2014it's honestly like stepping back in time. This car is in absolute pristine condition, practically flawless inside and out. It\u2019s been pampered in a garage and drives like a total dream, just like the day it was bought. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate a ride this perfect. Don't miss out on this gem!",
